lor:#6B7480; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; margin-bottom:10px;\">Team size<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:500; color:#fff;\">Finance, 5+<\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- RESULTS / PROOF -->\n  <div style=\"background:#F5F5F5; border-bottom:1px solid #EAEBED;\">\n    <div style=\"max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 40px;\">\n      <section style=\"padding:110px 0;\">\n        <div style=\"max-width:660px; margin-bottom:56px;\">\n          <span style=\"display:inline-block; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#1343F0; margin-bottom:16px;\">Proof, not promises<\u002Fspan>\n          <h2 style=\"font-size:clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.75rem); font-weight:500; line-height:1.12; letter-spacing:-0.02em;\">What changes in the first month.<\u002Fh2>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap:0; background:#EAEBED; border:1px solid #EAEBED;\">\n          <div style=\"background:#fff; padding:44px 34px;\">\n            <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n              <span style=\"font-size:1.75rem; font-weight:400; color:#9A9DA1; letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">30%<\u002Fspan>\n              <span style=\"font-size:1.25rem; color:#1343F0;\">→<\u002Fspan>\n              <span style=\"font-size:2.75rem; font-weight:500; color:#1343F0; letter-spacing:-0.02em; line-height:1;\">80%<\u002Fspan>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n            <h6 style=\"font-size:1.1875rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:8px;\">Daily active AI users in finance<\u002Fh6>\n            <p style=\"font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.55; color:#585E66;\">Share of the finance team using AI daily, one month after the workshop.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"background:#fff; padding:44px 34px;\">\n            