gap:72px; align-items:start;\">\n        <div>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-block; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#1343F0; margin-bottom:18px;\">The problem<\u002Fspan>\n          <h2 style=\"font-size:clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.75rem); font-weight:500; line-height:1.12; letter-spacing:-0.02em;\">Cut through the AI-in-finance hype and build only on what's already proven to work.<\u002Fh2>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0;\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex; gap:22px; padding:24px 0; border-top:1px solid #EAEBED;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:ui-monospace, monospace; font-size:0.875rem; font-weight:500; color:#1343F0; padding-top:3px;\">01<\u002Fspan>\n            <p style=\"color:#39424D; font-size:1.0625rem; line-height:1.55;\">Every reporting cycle turns into a scramble because the logic lives in someone's head, not in a system.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex; gap:22px; padding:24px 0; border-top:1px solid #EAEBED;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:ui-monospace, monospace; font-size:0.875rem; font-weight:500; color:#1343F0; padding-top:3px;\">02<\u002Fspan>\n            <p style=\"color:#39424D; font-size:1.0625rem; line-height:1.55;\">Generic AI training teaches prompting. Nobody leaves with something that actually runs Monday morning.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"display:flex; gap:22px; padding:24px 0; border-top:1px solid #EAEBED; border-bottom:1px solid #EAEBED;\">\n            <span style=\"font-family:ui-monospace, monospace; font-size:0.875rem; font-weight:500; color:#1343F0; padding-top:3px;\">03<\u002Fspan>\n            <p style=\"color:#39424D; font-size:1.0625rem; line-height:1.55;\">Tools get bought seat by seat, with no shared logic across the team and no one accountable for how they're used.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n