v style=\"border-left:1px solid #DFE0E2; padding-left:24px;\"><span style=\"display:block; font-size:0.7rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:#9A9DA1; margin-bottom:7px;\">You get<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:0.9375rem; color:#39424D;\">A sprint scoped exactly to your team, before we land<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n\n          <div style=\"position:relative; display:grid; grid-template-columns:150px 1.4fr 1fr; gap:44px; padding:30px 0; border-top:1px solid #E5E6E8;\">\n            <span style=\"position:absolute; left:-34px; top:36px; width:11px; height:11px; border-radius:50%; background:#1343F0; border:3px solid #F5F5F5;\"><\u002Fspan>\n            <div style=\"font-size:0.8125rem; color:#1343F0; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.03em; text-transform:uppercase; padding-top:5px;\">Morning<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div><h5 style=\"font-size:1.3125rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:9px; letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">Set-up &amp; governance<\u002Fh5><p style=\"font-size:1rem; line-height:1.55; color:#585E66;\">Claude accounts configured for finance-specific tasks. Finance context layer built — COA, KPI definitions, reporting logic. Guardrails agreed with the CFO before anyone touches live data.<\u002Fp><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"border-left:1px solid #DFE0E2; padding-left:24px;\"><span style=\"display:block; font-size:0.7rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:#9A9DA1; margin-bottom:7px;\">You leave with<\u002Fspan><span style=\"font-size:0.9375rem; color:#39424D;\">A governed environment, ready to build in<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n\n          <div style=\"position:relative; display:grid; grid-template-columns:150px 1.4fr 1fr; gap:44px; padding:30px 0; border-top:1px solid #E5E6E8;\">\n            <span style=\"position:absolute; left:-34px; top:36px; width:11px; height:11px; border-radius:50%; background:#1343F0; border:3px solid #F5F5F5;\"><\u002Fspan>\n            <div 