rgin-bottom:10px;\">Built by the founders of<\u002Fspan>\n            <h6 style=\"font-size:1.1875rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:4px;\">incro<\u002Fh6>\n            <p style=\"font-size:0.9375rem; color:#585E66;\">Boutique financial consulting<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"flex:1; min-width:220px;\">\n            <span style=\"display:block; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#1343F0; margin-bottom:10px; opacity:0;\">&nbsp;<\u002Fspan>\n            <h6 style=\"font-size:1.1875rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:4px;\">CFO Studio<\u002Fh6>\n            <p style=\"font-size:0.9375rem; color:#585E66;\">AI-powered financial analysis platform<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fsection>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- FIT + COMMITMENT -->\n  <div style=\"max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 40px;\">\n    <section style=\"padding:120px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap:72px;\">\n        <div>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-block; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#1343F0; margin-bottom:16px;\">Who this is for<\u002Fspan>\n          <h4 style=\"font-size:1.875rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:16px; letter-spacing:-0.015em; line-height:1.2;\">Finance functions of 5 or more.<\u002Fh4>\n          <p style=\"font-size:1.0625rem; line-height:1.6; color:#585E66;\">Enough scale for every seat to leave with their own agent — and for a monthly cadence to be worth running. Built for CFOs leading finance functions where reporting standards are high and there's no room for ungoverned AI.<\u002Fp>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-block; font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#1343F0; margin-bottom:16px;\">How it's structur