:16px;\">Questions<\u002Fspan>\n          <h2 style=\"font-size:clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.75rem); font-weight:500; line-height:1.12; letter-spacing:-0.02em;\">Before you book the call<\u002Fh2>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; max-width:820px; margin:0 auto;\">\n          <div style=\"padding:30px 0; border-top:1px solid #DFE0E2;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:1.1875rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:12px; letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">What if our team isn't at 5 people yet?<\u002Fdiv>\n            <p style=\"font-size:1rem; line-height:1.6; color:#585E66; max-width:680px;\">The workshop is built around a per-person agent build, so it works best once a finance function has the headcount to make that — and the monthly cadence after — worth running. Reach out anyway; we'll tell you honestly if it's a fit.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:30px 0; border-top:1px solid #DFE0E2;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:1.1875rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:12px; letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">Why not just have a developer build this?<\u002Fdiv>\n            <p style=\"font-size:1rem; line-height:1.6; color:#585E66; max-width:680px;\">A developer builds you an agent. They don't teach your controller to build the next five, modify them, and trust them. After the workshop, your team ships new workflows without looping in IT. And we bring something a developer can't: finance domain expertise and technical build in the same person.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:30px 0; border-top:1px solid #DFE0E2;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:1.1875rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:12px; letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">Do materials and support stay with us after the bootcamp?<\u002Fdiv>\n            <p style=\"font-size:1rem; line-height:1.6; color:#585E66; max-width:680px;\">Everything — guidebooks, prompt templates, session recordings, usage standards — stays with your team, since the agents are built together, not handed over. Ongoing options after week 4 include monthly AI Champion support, update sessions tied to new Claude releases, or a standalone advisory project for more complex agents.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"padding:30px 0; border-top:1px solid #DFE0E2; border-bottom:1px solid #DFE0E2;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:1.1875rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:12px; letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">Is this vendor-neutral, or tied to a specific tool?<\u002Fdiv>\n            <p style=\"font-size:1rem; line-height:1.6; color:#585E66; max-width:680px;\">The workshop is built specifically around the Claude ecosystem — chat, Cowork, Code, Skills, and Claude for Excel/PowerPoint — because that's what we've tested deeply enough to teach with rigor, not because we're reselling licenses.<\u002Fp>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fsection>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- CLOSING CTA -->\n  <div id=\"contact\" style=\"background:#020A14; color:#fff; position:relative; overflow:hidden;\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:-260px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:680px; height:680px; background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(19,67,240,0.2), transparent 66%); filter:blur(30px); pointer-events:none;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 40px; position:relative; z-index:1;\">\n      <section style=\"padding:120px 0; text-align:center;\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size:clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 3rem); font-weight:500; line-height:1.1; letter-spacing:-0.025em; color:#fff; margin-bottom:18px;\">One day to build it. A year to master it.<\u002Fh2>\n        <p style=\"font-size:1.1875rem; line-height:1.6; color:#9AA3AE; max-width:560px; margin:0 auto 38px;\">One 30-minute call is enough to design the session, pick the agents, and agree the timeline.<\u002Fp>\n        <a href=\"https://www.incro.io/contact\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:16px 30px; background:#1343F0; color:#fff; font-size:1.0625rem; font-weight:500; border-radius:2px; border:1px solid #1343F0;\" style-hover=\"background:#2B56F0; border-color:#2B56F0;\">Book a discovery call →<\u002Fa>\n      <\u002Fsection>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <!-- FOOTER (simplified) -->\n  <footer style=\"background:#020A14; color:#fff; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n    \n    <div style=\"max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:20px 40px; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n      <p style=\"font-size:0.8125rem; color:#6B7480;\">© 2026 incro · AI in Finance Workshop<\u002Fp>\n      <a href=\"https://incro.pl/privacy-policy\" style=\"font-size:0.8125rem; color:#6B7480;\" style-hover=\"color:#9AA3AE;\">Privacy Policy<\u002Fa>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Ffooter>\n\n<\u002Fdiv>\n<\u002Fx-dc>\n<script type=\"text/x-dc\" data-dc-script=\"\" data-props=\"{\n  &quot;showAnnouncement&quot;: {&quot;editor&quot;:&quot;boolean&quot;,&quot;default&quot;:false,&quot;tsType&quot;:&quot;boolean&quot;,&quot;section&quot;:&quot;Announcement bar&quot;},\n  &quot;announcementText&quot;: {&quot;editor&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;default&quot;:&quot;Cohort 2 now booking&quot;,&quot;tsType&quot;:&quot;string&quot;,&quot;section&quot;:&quot;Announcement bar&quot;},\n  &quot;announcementHighlight&quot;: {&quot;editor&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;default&quot;:&quot;limited on-site spots for Q3 2026&quot;,&quot;tsType&quot;:&quot;string&quot;,&quot;section&quot;:&quot;Announcement bar&quot;},\n  &quot;contactEmail&quot;: {&quot;editor&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;default&quot;:&quot;hello@incro.pl&quot;,&quot;tsType&quot;:&quot;string&quot;,&quot;section&quot;:&quot;Contact&quot;}\n}\">\nclass Component extends DCLogic {\n  renderVals(){\n    const email = this.props.contactEmail || 'hello@incro.pl';\n    return {\n      showAnnouncement: this.props.showAnnouncement ?? false,\n      announcementText: this.props.announcementText || 'Cohort 2 now booking',\n      announcementHighlight: this.props.announcementHighlight || 'limited on-site spots for Q3 2026',\n      email,\n      mailto: 'mailto:' + email\n    };\n  }\n}\n<\u002Fscript>\n\n\n<\u002Fbody><\u002Fhtml>"
